516→+
517→+**When to apply:** New CLI commands, MCP tools, configuration options, or other features that end users interact with directly.
518→+
519→+**Detection:**
520→+```bash
521→+# Detect user-facing changes
522→+cli_added=$(git diff main...HEAD -- bin/cli.ts | grep -E '^\+.*\.command\(' | wc -l | xargs || true)
