532→+**If user-facing changes detected, answer these questions:**
533→+
534→+| Question | What to check |
535→+|----------|---------------|
536→+| **First-time setup:** Can a new user go from zero to working? | List every prerequisite. Try the setup path mentally. |
537→+| **Per-environment differences:** Does this work the same everywhere? | macOS/Linux/Windows, different clients/tools, CI vs local |
538→+| **What does the user see?** | Walk through the actual UX — wait times, output format, progress indicators |
539→+| **What happens after?** | Where's the output? What does the user do next? |
540→+| **Failure modes the user will hit:** | Not code edge cases — real scenarios (wrong directory, missing auth, timeout) |
